{
  "stem": "24830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were the killer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like me, I never wear a gun, you know, to have-- but we decided to-- to do something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was all for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you used to knew who they were and-- and look for the way they live, where they live, what they do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the-- the two worst one-- one was kill and the other-- when-- when they-- I-- oh, I forget to tell you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I was in-- in-- in school, there was-- I was-- I had a friend who live with a Russian, a white Russian.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he knew me, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one day, when I change my name, he saw me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, oh, Michelin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Where-- where do you live now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I was very uncomfortable-- with friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He say, why don't you come and live with us?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's very, very safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You won't have to worried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, I saw my friend, this-- this woman from-- from art school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she's in bicycle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's all in black.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I say, what's the matter with you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, they kill him-- I mean, him-- George.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I say, why they kill him?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, they say he did something wrong, but it's not true, and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was bothered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I met everybody in the evening, I say, well, who did you kill?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, the worst one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it-- this was that man who asked me to go live-- to go and live with them, Serge.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Serge, his name was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, people like me-- young people, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were mostly my age, maybe a little older.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most-- the worst one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after from-- 1,000, maybe, I don't know-- a month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It came down to 100.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
